With this simple extension you have the possibility to adjust the video playback rate above the usual maximum (2). It introduces 2 more steps (3 and 4).

It usually only focuses on the very first video element on the page however the context menu options allows to adjust any video element on a page to be adjusted. Simply right click on the video and adjust it however you want. ü§ù
